library(tidyverse)
library(tsibbledata)
library(lubridate)
library(ggplot2)
library(leaflet)

nyc_bikes_df <- nyc_bikes

nyc_bikes_df
nyc_bikes_df <- nyc_bikes_df %>% 
  mutate(day = day(start_time),
         month = month(start_time),label = TRUE, abbr = FALSE,
          year = year(start_time))

nyc_bikes_df <- nyc_bikes_df %>% 
  mutate(age = (year - birth_year))


view(nyc_bikes_df)
#durationtravel
nyc_bikes_df <- nyc_bikes_df %>% 
  mutate(duration_bike = as.duration(start_time - stop_time))

nyc_bikes_df %>% 
  group_by(day) %>% 
  count() %>% 
  summarise(n)
nyc_bikes_df %>% 
  group_by(day) %>% 
  count() %>% 
  summarise(n) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x= day, y = n))+
  geom_point()+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = 1:31)+
  theme_bw()+
  labs(x = "Monthly days",
       y = "Number of users",
       title =" Our Clients")
